               <p>NEW COURT. WEDNESDAY, APRIL 13.</p>
               <p>Fifth Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
               <p>972. 
               
                  <persName id="t18310407-277-defend1909" type="defendantName">
                     JAMES 
                     SMITH
                  <interp inst="t18310407-277-defend1909" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310407-277-defend1909" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>
